title: #92Noon! 11am Hour 2/21 - Kevin Gorg, Questions for Lavelle
description: Nordo goes through what would’ve been his questions for a flying Lavelle E Neal, Kevin Gorg joins to continue the puck talk and preview the rest of the Wild road trip, and Nordo goes through the recent Vikes hires.
